<exercise checkit-seed="0005" checkit-slug="F2" checkit-title="Compound Interest">
  <statement>
                <p>Marie invests $1080 in a bank account that pays
                3.6% compounded weekly for 7 years. 
                    <ol>
                      <li>How much money will they have at the end?</li>
                      <li>How much interest did they earn?</li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
      
      
      <p>

      </p>
      
  </statement>
    
  <answer>
            <p>
              <ol>
                <li>They will have <m>P_0 (1 + \frac{r}{n})^{nt} = 1080(1 + \frac{0.036}{52})^{52\cdot 7} = </m> $1,389.4 overall.</li>
                <li><m>FV - P_0 = 1389.4 - 1080 = </m> $309.4 in interest was generated.</li>
              </ol>
            </p>
      
  </answer>
</exercise>
